\f0\b\fs34 \cf0 Irish Cream
\b0 \uc0\u8232 Makes 1 bottle \u8232 1 cup Irish whiskey\u8232 1 (14 ounce) can Eagle Brand condensed milk\u8232 1 cup whipping cream (the real stuff)\u8232 4 eggs\u8232 2 tablespoons chocolate flavored syrup (like Monin)\u8232 2 teaspoon instant coffee granules\u8232 2 teaspoon vanilla extract\u8232 \u8232 Combine all ingredients then blend until smooth. Store in a tightly covered container in refrigerator. You can serve it in 24 hours. It\'92ll last a month just stir before serving.
