\f0\b\fs34 Coffee Liqueur
\b0 \uc0\u8232 Makes 2 bottles \u8232 5 cups sugar\u8232 8 cups water\u8232 1 1/4 cups instant coffee\u8232 6 tablespoons Vanilla extract\u8232 1/2 bottle (750 ml) vodka\u8232 \u8232 Heat the sugar and the water to boiling then remove it from the heat and leave to cool. When at room temperature mix it with all the other ingredients and bottle it. Let it sit undisturbed in a cool dark place for one month.
